<paragraph blockId="8.[163,1070,1056,1137]" pageId="8" pageNumber="1265">
E t y m o l o g y: The species is named in honour to Prof. Dr. Pierre Rasmont from Mons University in 
<collectingCountry box="[315,405,1085,1107]" name="Belgium" pageId="8" pageNumber="1265">Belgium</collectingCountry>
, a leading expert for bumblebees and other bee genera, and entomological expert of the 
<taxonomicName authority="O. Rabat" authorityName="Schmid" authorityYear="2021" box="[448,545,1115,1136]" genus="Icarda" pageId="8" pageNumber="1266" rank="genus" status="N.G.">ICARDA</taxonomicName>
project.
</paragraph>
